{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_01","textHome":"什么？如果想组个魔法少女好朋友@小队的话……抱歉，能去找别人吗？我啊，@已经决定无论什么时候，都只为自己使用@魔法了。在战场上碰面的话还请多指教。@赌上猎物……堂堂正正的比试吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_18","textHome":"我发现了。@玩到最后啊，乐谱都可以背下来了。@所以这个还能锻炼大脑哦。@怎么样？你也试着跳一曲吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_19","textHome":"嗯，我感觉到了，状态不错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_20","textHome":"这种感觉，真是不错……@不如去随便干一场吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_21","textHome":"看到和我一样为了傻事而许愿的家伙@我就气不打一处来。不过……@像我一样的人……我是没法放着不管的啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_22","textHome":"已经许过愿的事就没法回头了。@所以我也希望……那些为了他人@而成为魔法少女的人……@能迎来幸福的结局。@那样的话，我也算是得到拯救了吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_23","textHome":"有为了他人而许愿，最后得到幸福的人……@也有为了自己而许愿……只落得悲惨下场的人……@所以……我不用去后悔那一天我许下的愿望。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_24","textHome":"太～慢～了！真是的，我等了好久。@那么，我们走吧！@……等等，你来之前……吃饭了吗？@如果还没有的话……那要吃这个吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_25","textHome":"啊——好困……你怎么从一大早@就这么精神……啊，对了！@那你去给我做早饭吧。拜托你了！@在你做好之前，我再睡会儿……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_26","textHome":"好，该午饭啦午饭！吃什么好呢！@日式……还是中餐……咖喱也不错啊……@还是狠狠心吃烤肉呢？@啊——决定不了啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_27","textHome":"那么……就稍微陪我去游戏厅玩会儿吧。@不要小看游戏。@游戏对爆发力的锻炼是很有效的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_03","textHome":"越是单纯的人……@是不是就越容易受伤啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_28","textHome":"我喜欢漫步在夜晚的街道。@这样做每次都能让我明白……@人们都是孤独的……@没什么，刚刚是开玩笑的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_29","textHome":"我可是一天二十四小时都做好了战斗的准备，@所以发生什么都不要紧。@随便敌人从哪个地方冒出来我都不怕！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_30","textHome":"……那么 ，在你打瞌睡的时候，@我就出个门吧。@猎物数量有限，先下手为强嘛。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_31","textHome":"诶～你想和我战斗？有意思！来吧来吧！@不用顾虑，用全力攻过来吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_32","textHome":"真是聚集了好多人啊～@不过不管和谁战斗，我都不会输。@想较量的话，就做好准备来吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_33","textHome":"想要兼任魔法少女和学生真的很难。@到最后，只能牺牲玩游戏的时间了吧？@明明和我同年的家伙们都在外面疯玩。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_34","textHome":"食物是人类生存的关键对吧？@不过现在的人大多数都沉溺在@眼前的幸福之中，早就忘记了这回事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_35","textHome":"在战斗中，还有头脑战这么一说吧？@制定战术也是很重要的。@所以我总是会用甜食来补充糖分。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_36","textHome":"不要光看着……下次你也来试试嘛，跳舞机。@呵呵，是呀。@你慌慌张张的样子肯定很有意思。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_37","textHome":"蛋糕店的蛋糕真是精致啊……@虽然父亲在世的时候我也没吃过几次。@不过……对我来说依然是充满回忆的味道。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_04","textHome":"不知道已经多久……@没有在这么时髦的饭店里吃饭了啊？@真好吃。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_38","textHome":"总感觉有些饿了呢……说起来，我听沙耶香说@车站附近有家很美味的拉面店……@好，那就去看看吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_39","textHome":"小圆她啊，虽然平常总是软绵绵的样子，@但到了关键时刻却非常有骨气。@真是人不可貌相啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_40","textHome":"唔——总感觉沙耶香没有我看着@就会做出很危险的事来……@真是的，就很让人没办法啊……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_41","textHome":"一个人的话……很寂寞吧。@没问题，我来陪你吧……@你以为我会这样娇惯你吗！@快快快，拿出气势！打起精神来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_42","textHome":"那么就放手大干一场吧！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_43","textHome":"这场胜利归我了。"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_44","textHome":"战果很不错！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_45","textHome":"好啦，要吃什么呢——"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_46","textHome":"打败敌人了！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_63","textHome":"交给我吧！这里就由我来解决！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_05","textHome":"竟然送我花……呵呵。@我真是遇到了可爱的魔女啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_64","textHome":"就用这招结束这场战斗……！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_65","textHome":"别在我眼前跳来跳去了，蠢货！"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_66","textHome":"就用这招让你闭嘴……！盟神抉枪!!@哈啊啊啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_02","textHome":"我是佐仓杏子，幸会。@想和我一起战斗的话，就请我吃顿晚饭吧？@……开个玩笑。午饭就可以啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":200600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_13","textHome":"嗯，感觉还算不错。就这样继续吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_14","textHome":"好！到了这一步，@就该考虑下个阶段该怎么办了，对吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_15","textHome":"每个人都有不同的故事……@那么，这就是我的故事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_16","textHome":"我的性格就是要做就要做到最好。@就算是最高难度我也要完美通关。@哈？当然是在说跳舞机啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_17","textHome":"因为要追上不断从上面掉下来的音符，@所以我的动态视力也得到了锻炼，@对战斗也会有帮助哦。@嗯，说的就是跳舞机。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}]},"version":2}